జై (గోపిచంద్) ఒక నిజాయితీ గల ఫైర్ ఆఫీసర్. తన కుటుంబంతో కలిసి ఆనందంగా జీవిస్తుంటాడు. ఈ క్రమంలో సావిత్రి (రాశి ఖన్నా)ను ప్రేమించి, ఆమెతో మధురమైన క్షణాలు గడుపుతాడు. అండర్‌వర్ల్డ్ డాన్ చోటా నాయక్ (కబీర్) జైతో ఎదురుపడతాడు. వారిద్దరి మధ్య ఒక చిన్న తప్పు పెద్ద యుద్ధంగా మారుతుంది. మిగతా కథలో జై తన సమస్యలు ఎలా పరిష్కరించాడు? చోటా నాయక్‌ను ఎలా ఎదుర్కొన్నాడు? అనేదే మిగిలిన భాగం.

Aussie YouTube Channel "Ok Aussie" with Dyan Linley Moore & Matt.

Subscribe for daily life, GRWM, vlogging, jokes, fun, comedy, hauls, shopping, coffee chats, podcast & antics of Dyan.

An Aussie Vlogger who's an Autistic & ADHD YouTuber & Advocate, along with her partner Matt, Ragdoll Cats Willow, Max born & bred in Australia. 

Subscribe to Ok Aussie!

Dyan has a life shortening by 25 to 30 years & life-threatening rare genetic chromosomal syndrome "22q" or more fully known as 22q11.2 Deletion Syndrome and is vlogging her daily life of a disabled girl living her best life simple, peaceful & authentically. Life is short & her passion for experiences is huge so her zest for life huge. Her love of her son's has always been a special part of her more healthier life. Our sons love her just as much. Now her focus is her roots of being in nature & her dream is to travel van life before it's too late. Dyan is a free spirit and has always held that up. Travel is her roots. 

In our vlogs you will enjoy Shopping Hauls, Genuine Product Reviews, Resin Art Projects, Home Decorating, Shein Hauls, GRWM, Get Ready With Me, DITL Day In The Life, Weekly Updates, Disability Living, Morning Routine, Night Routine, Coffee Chats, Cooking Vlogs, Craft & Sewing, Comedy, Funny Shorts, Stories, Podcasts & Places We Go! 

We love showing our Aussie life! 

We are a dedicated channel to deliver daily vlogs, good, bad & ugly! We hope to show you a great future that just needs to be planned. Life is what you make it. We are all friends here! ❤️

Subscribe to Ok Aussie & we will be so glad to see you here!

Please Like, Subscribe and Click the Notification Bell!
